				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hiya! Here is a good quest for newbies to do. It get's you a coif to wear on your head! <BR>
<BR>
Shestar's Scaled Coif<BR>
Quest, Lore Item<BR>
WHERE: Kunark, East Cabilis (Trooper Shestar)<BR>
AC: 4<BR>
WT:0.8<BR>
SLOT: Head<BR>
CLASS: WAR CLR PAL RNG SHD DRU MNK BRD ROG SHM<BR>
RACE: ALL<BR>
PRICE: Merchant will pay around 1 gold 9 silver 9 copper for it...<BR>
<BR>
*First, Talk to Trooper Shestar...<BR>
<BR>
You say 'Hail Trooper Shestar.'<BR>
Trooper Shestar says 'My father was a great blacksmith. He taught me how to make great items such as the [Shestar Scaled Coif]. Alas, smithing was not my rebirth, but rather the life of a warrior.'<BR>
You say 'What is the Shestar Scaled Coif?'<BR>
Trooper Shestar says 'The Shestar Scaled Coif was a light coif my father would fashion out of loose scales from the scaled wolves. I have some scales on me and if you bring me three loose scales I will have enough to create the coif for you, but I require you also pay a fee of five gold.'<BR>
<BR>
Second, Collect the 3 loose scales from the scaled wolves and the 5 gold. Then take them back to Trooper Shestar and give them to him... ***Do not stack the loose scales***<BR>
<BR>
Trooper Shestar says 'I asked for three loose wolf scales and my fee of five gold.'<BR>
Trooper Shestar says 'I asked for three loose wolf scales and my fee of five gold.'<BR>
Trooper Shestar says 'I asked for three loose wolf scales and my fee of five gold.'<BR>
Trooper Shestar quickly inserts the scales into a half finished coif and hands you the coif. 'I am afraid that is not enough and I cannot possibly complete the tast while on duty. You must go and find an additional tree scaled wolf scales and take them, along with the unfinished coif, to the nearest forge and complete the smithing yourself. I hope you are a blacksmith.'<BR>
<BR>
Thrid, Get 3 more scaled wolf scales and talk them to the forge along with the unfinished coif. ***Do not stack the loose scales*** Combine and you have the Shestar's Scaled Coif!<BR>
<BR>
The Scaled Wolves can be found in The Feild of Bones. Here are two maps to help you...<BR>
<BR>
http://www.geocities.com/skankgurl101/map.gif<BR>
http://www.eqatlas.com/kunark/cabilis.html<BR>
<BR>
Jazakia<BR>
Iksar Warrior<BR>
